## Platform Overview

KoreShield provides enterprise-grade security for Large Language Model (LLM) applications through a comprehensive set of features designed to protect, monitor, and manage AI interactions.

::github{repo="koreshield/koreshield"}

## Core Security Features

### Content Security

{% callout type="important" %}
KoreShield's content security layer provides real-time protection against malicious inputs and outputs.
{% /callout %}

- **Jailbreak Detection**: Advanced algorithms identify and block attempts to bypass LLM safety measures
- **Prompt Injection Prevention**: Real-time monitoring prevents malicious prompt injection attacks
- **Sensitive Data Filtering**: Automatically detects and sanitizes PII, credentials, and confidential information

### Usage Monitoring

{% callout type="note" %}
Comprehensive logging and analytics provide visibility into all LLM interactions.
{% /callout %}

- **Request/Response Logging**: Complete audit trail of all LLM API calls
- **Analytics Dashboard**: Real-time insights into usage patterns and security events  
- **Alerting System**: Configurable alerts for suspicious activities and anomalies

## Multi-Provider Support

KoreShield offers a unified API interface for multiple LLM providers:

- **OpenAI** (GPT-4, GPT-3.5)
- **Anthropic** (Claude 3 Opus, Sonnet, Haiku)
- **Google** (Gemini Pro, Gemini Ultra)
- **Azure OpenAI** (Enterprise deployments)

{% callout type="tip" %}
Switch between providers without changing your application code.
{% /callout %}

