### Real-Time Monitoring
- Live security event dashboard
- Request/response inspection tools
- Performance metrics and analytics

### Policy Management
- Custom security rules and policies
- Provider failover configuration
- Rate limiting and quota management

### Reporting & Analytics
- Compliance reports (SOC2, HIPAA, GDPR)
- Usage analytics and trends
- Security incident summaries

## Developer Experience

KoreShield is designed with developers in mind:

### Easy Integration
```python
# Drop-in replacement for OpenAI SDK
from koreshield import KoreShield

client = KoreShield(api_key="your-key")
response = client.chat.completions.create(
    model="gpt-4",
    messages=[{"role": "user", "content": "Hello!"}]
)
```

### SDKs Available
- **Python**: `pip install koreshield`
- **JavaScript/TypeScript**: `npm install @koreshield/sdk`
- **REST API**: Direct HTTP access

### Documentation
Comprehensive guides and API references at [koreshield.com/docs](https://koreshield.com/docs)

## Getting Started

1. Sign up at [koreshield.com](https://koreshield.com)
2. Get your API key from the dashboard
3. Install your preferred SDK
4. Start securing your LLM applications

